      <title>土耳其限制进出伊斯坦布尔以遏制抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/turkey-limits-travel-in-and-out-of-istanbul-to-curb-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其对该国最大的城市伊斯坦布尔施加了旅行限制，以遏制因拘留著名的反对派政治家的拘留而引发的反政府抗议活动的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/turkey-limits-travel-in-and-out-of-istanbul-to-curb-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 19:55:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FEMA灾难工作者需要国土安全部长的批准才能继续工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/fema-disaster-workers-need-secretary-s-approval-to-stay-on-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数联邦紧急事务管理局的雇员将需要国土安全部长克里斯蒂·诺姆（Kristi Noem）的批准才能在目前的任期到期后继续担任这项工作，这为唐纳德·特朗普总统寻求缩小联邦机构而大大减少人员铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/fema-disaster-workers-need-secretary-s-approval-to-stay-on-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 17:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳米比亚的新总统名称witbooi为副手，修剪机柜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/namibia-s-new-president-names-witbooi-as-deputy-trims-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳米比亚总统Netumbo Nandi-Ndaitwah任命了长期服务的议员Lucia Witbooi为她的副手，因为她揭露了一个精简的内阁，巩固了关键的部门，并将石油和天然气放在自己的办公室下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/namibia-s-new-president-names-witbooi-as-deputy-trims-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 17:17:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划以更有针对性的推动计划他的关税“解放日”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-plans-his-tariff-liberation-day-with-more-targeted-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）即将来临的关税浪潮有望比他偶尔威胁的弹幕，助手和盟友说，这可能会使市场受到对全面关税战争的焦虑感的潜在缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-plans-his-tariff-liberation-day-with-more-targeted-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的选举取决于谁可以在美国威胁下解决经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/canada-s-election-to-be-fought-on-who-can-fix-an-economy-under-us-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）预计将在周日闯入加拿大的竞选活动，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trade War）的贸易战使重点放在解决妨碍加拿大经济的长期问题上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/canada-s-election-to-be-fought-on-who-can-fix-an-economy-under-us-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 16:23:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉说，美国遣返航班将在周日恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/venezuela-says-us-repatriation-flights-to-resume-after-accord</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉顶级官员说，在两国政府之间达成协议后，从美国驱逐出境的航班将在周日恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/venezuela-says-us-repatriation-flights-to-resume-after-accord</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 15:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
