      <title>印度运营商拒绝监管机构在酿造TIFF时的数据请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/indian-carriers-refuse-regulator-s-data-request-in-brewing-tiff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的航空公司拒绝分享政府监管机构寻求的机票数据，与他们试图改善几乎垄断的市场中消费者的保护措施的政策制定者发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/indian-carriers-refuse-regulator-s-data-request-in-brewing-tiff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 14:53:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国得到预算警告，因为DBRS评级为负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/france-gets-budget-warning-as-dbrs-turns-negative-on-rating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Morningstar DBRS对法国信誉的评估产生了负面的看法，这增加了对国防支出的需求日益增长的要求和持续存在政治不稳定风险的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/france-gets-budget-warning-as-dbrs-turns-negative-on-rating</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 13:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
